Text: *the grocery bag-clad, pink pony hops along, leaving a trail of snowy hoofprints on her wake*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Whew, not THAT'S what I call a catnap! ^.^ *she giggles and leans over, the crate toppling on top of her*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text:
Zzzzzzzzz-*SNORT!* *Pinkie abruptly sneezes a load of confetti out of the nap box*
WHOWHATWHEREHOW- *her shrunken eyes dart about*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Zzzzzzz....... *the pink pony's back hooves waggle slowly as she naps away*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: RT @MLP_Trixie : Sorry it's come to this. https://t.co/mgDjQlqqdL
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she snorts and rolls over*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *an overindulged, Hearth's Warming'd Pinkie sleeps soundly near the small fireplace in the upstairs of SCC. The lack of moonlight outside causes the room to have a cozy glow*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: @mlp_Rainbow ((Night, Dash!))
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: ((I need to hop AFK for a bit. Have fun, everyone! ^.^))
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *as she stuffs the remaining treat in her maw, Pinkie bounces over to a @mlp_Rainbow and tells her that @mlp_SIlverS_ is on the hunt for her*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the flash of color immediately catches her attention. Grinning, the pink pony hops up toward the snack table and grabs the nearest festive brownie*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Awww, thank you, @MLP_Lyndis; I hope they help you go and be as merry as you can! ^.^
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie does a 360 bou cent spin and shakes her head* Not yet, @mlp_SilverS_, but if and when she sneaks in, I'll send her your way! ^.^
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Hiya, Lyndis! *she smiles at @MLP_Lyndis* I hope you like what @mlp_Equality, @MLP_Shimmery, and I threw together!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Told you we'd be fine! ^.^ *she stretches over and nudges @mlp_Equality. Pinkie wavey-wavea at @mlp_SilverS_, @mlp_MagnifyingG, @MLP_Lyndis, and @mlp__smolder*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Happy Birthday, Twilight, wherever you are! ^.^
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *her ears, and tail, twitch as she giggles* Got 'em!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *for the entirety of her day, Pinkie has busily been rigging up @mlp_Twilight's frequent visiting areas with tons of proxy party cannons*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *her preparations for @mlp_Twilight's party have been vast and expansive. So much so that she's refused to let even a whisper of it escape*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: ((I'm going to address tonight. The previous incidents weren't enough for people to catch on, so I'll make this clear: if you associate with Ian, you're being blocked. His behavior has been allowed to get to this point with almost no repercussions, and I find this unacceptable.))
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text:
*having wrapped up the winners, Pinkie hops off into the AFKrowd and blends in*

((Huge thank you to everyone who came by and played in #RotL19! It was lots of fun!))
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: And to everyone else, you all did a super great job! Those trees are looking bare and ready for winter and scarfing! ^.^ #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: And now, for our gold medal winner! *Pinkie stuffs the clipboard in her manepoof* In first place, we have none other than... @mlp_Emberscales! Congrats to you, too! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Our silver medal winner is... *Pinkie snickers* @mlp_SilverS_! That's pretty fitting if you ask me! Congrats! ^.^ #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: And now, our top three! *Pinkie holds the clipboard close* Our bronze medal winner is none other than @mlp_Elysium! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Now, for our awesome top 5 racers! *she beams* In 5th, we have @mlp_Starbeats, and our 4th place winner is @mlp_StrawberryB! Congrats, you two! ^.^ #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: In 7th, we have @mlp_Heartstroke, and our 6th place winner iiiiiiis..... @mlp_Louie! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Now, for our racers, in 10th, we haveeeeee.... *Pinkie skims down* @mlp_Hoofstorm, 9th we have @mlp_Pistachio, and in 8th, we have......@mlp_generallee! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Starting from our special, new award, for the best cheering during the race, we have... @mlp_Gallus! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Okie dokey! *the judges finish with the word 'Jahu', pass her a taped-up clipboard, and hops off toward the beginning of the track* #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the pink pony bounces off toward the judges and leans in on their murmurs. She blinks at the word 'Khra'* #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie arcs the balloon toward the ground, hops out, and ties to around a nearby rock* Oooooh, now this is gonna definitely be a close one! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: They're almost there, and-and the winner is...- *the abrupt crossing of the sardine-racers kicks up a dust cloud large enough to cover...everything!* #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Now from behind, we've got @mlp_SilverBulet, @mlp_Plotline, and co. Oh, this is beyond photo. We're gonna have a...canvas finish! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Don't count @mlp_Generallee or @mlp_StrawberryB out yet though, because they're coming on fast! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Our front clump is a mix of @mlp_Rainbow, @mlp_Applejack, @mlp_SilverS_, @mlp_Emberscales, @mlp_Starbeats, @mlp_Elysium and... the @mlp_UngooseAlt! Others are super close behind! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *despite the low altitude, she's got her sattention trained on the front* OOOOOH, FINAL STRETCH! Things are about to get intense! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Why not ask her yourself? *she smiles at @mlp_Birdcat and gestures toward @mlp_StrawberryB* #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Good choice! *nodding at @mlp_Birdcat, Pinkie arcs the balloon down toward @mlp_StrawberryB and floats just above the ground* #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Up ahead, we have our second bridge, then our final stretch. If you want to make up ground, now's the best time! ^.^ #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: But enough about that, we're almost at the 2/3 mark! Gooooooooo racers! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Oh, you're SO right, @mlp_Birdcat, and I'm sure a certain honey-bear and secret honey-loving pony would totally LOVE it right now! ^.^ #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Don't trip here, racers, or you're in for a world of pancake breakfasts with no end in sight! *she giggles* #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the pink pony looks ahead* And for the few lucky creatures just now getting through, we're coming up to Syrup 2, Maple Boogaloo with Sweet Maple Orchards. Not sponsored, by the way! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *her mane curls up, a few strands turning white. PInkie rolls up a news paper and shouts* And we have a colorful development below involving bees and a VERY hyper creature! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Wow, that's a BIG swarm! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Whew! *Pinkie peeks down at the...slightly angry hive* Ahem... *she passes the megaphone to @mlp_Birdcat* #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Oh well, you can pick another one, BirdCaaa-AAAAAAAAAA! *Pinkie practically pulls the rope free of the basin as she maneuvers the balloon above the beehive* #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Good choice, @mlp_Birdcat; @drwhooves always has good commen-- and they're gone! *Pinkie blinks as they seemingly meld in with the runners* #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Before we get to the bees and their ten new hives! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *her eyes shrink at the sudden 'uh oh'* I think it's about time to go down to the scene! *Pinkie peeks over at @mlp_Birdcat* Do you wanna pick our next racer before everyone crosses the bridge? #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: You can't beat the stumps freshness, @mlp_Birdcat! *she peeks over the edge* It looks like a few racers have pulled up to the end of the stumps, but lucky for them, the bridges were redone last month, and made even nicer and narrower than before! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: And we aaaaaaall know what the means: maple syrup and sticky leaves! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: No time, because we're approaching the stumps! *she abruptly pulls the rope and soars up above the treeline* #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: It's like sardines, or saltwater taffy! *Pinkie smiles* @mlp_Emberscales, how's it feel that you've got a goose on you? ^.^ #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: And we're getting some first hoofaccounts of fowl play between @mlp_UngooseAlt and @mlp_Emberscales! Let's get a closer look! *Pinkie swings the balloon down to just above the rocks* #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Looks like @mlp_generallee can't catch a break today as the rocks really rough up his rump! *she gigglesnorts* What about on your end, @mlp_Birdcat? #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie squints at @mlp_UnGooseAlt* aaaaaaand now there's a goose. *Pinkie takes a deep breath* WATCH YOUR POCKETS AROUND THE ROCKS, RACERS! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Oof, and down he goes! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: We've got @mlp_SilverS_, @mlp_Rebel, and @mlp_Starbeats heading toward the front, but the apple demon @mlp_Applejack is close behind, but wait, @mlp_Emberscales is trailing back! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: GO! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Get seeeeeeeeeet..... #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: On your marks.... #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text:
*whipping out her megaphone, Pinkie drops a few sandbags and drifts to the skies above, @mlp_BirdCat in tow* 
Racers, standby for Leaffall! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Climb aboard, skipper! *she grins at @mlp_Birdcat, beckoning* We're about to start it up! #RotL19
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she ignites the small fire basin under the balloon and watches as it quickly rises to life*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Oh, hiya @mlp_BirdCat! ^.^ *the pink pony tumbles over into the poorly hidden basket* Are you exciiiiiiited?!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Good luck, @mlp_Rarity! ^.^ *she wavey-waves to the fashionpone, bounces over to a nearby bush, and hops through*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Exactly three!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Mmmmm, all the time, @mlp_Rarity, but I don't buy it! *she grins* Do you know how many creatures want a hot air balloon to do commentary from?!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Aww, you worry too much. *she waves a hoof at @mlp_Rarity* I wouldn't miss this for all the ice cream in Equestria!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: You didn't check to your leeeeeft! *she sing-songs to @mlp_Rarity*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: MRRRRZMMMBRQ!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *moments later, her face greens a bit, her tongue droops out, and her muzzle is firmly snug into a nearby can of funfetti icing*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Hmmmm, tastes like @mlp_GummyGator's toothpaste!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *happy that @mlp_SilverS_ approves this time, Pinkie hums a high pitched hum as she licks a small chunk of icing off her snoot*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: And heeeeeeeere we are! *she stretches over the counter* Silver Streaaaaammmmmm, your Seacakes are reaaaaaaady! *the pink pony sing-songs in @mlp_SilverS_ and @mlp_Rocky's general direction*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Whew! HothotHOOOOOT! *Pinkie spills the cakes onto a small, circular plate and slings the hot tray into the sink. SSSSSSSSSS!*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie pulls out the green, chunky spatula just as the oven DINGS! She pulls out the tray, sets them down, and liberally coats the top of each treat*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *a quiet burp echoes from her tail as the fish pops out, completely descaled. She drops it in a small bowl and scoops out a helping of seaweed icing*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she gives the large bowl a final mix, pours it into the cupcake molds, and slides it in the oven with a metallic clang*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie holds the fish chunk over her tailor. It snaps up and absorbs the unfortunate piece of fish*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie slides the bowl down her back, hops over to the ice box, and whips out the lower half of a fish. Whistling, she breaks off a medium sized chunk and tosses the seafood back in*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *as she stirs in an egg, her tail coils around the oven knob and turns it to the left. Turning around, Pinkie cups her cheeks with flour-coated hooves*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *when nobody's looking, Pinkie sneakily scoops in just a pinch of salt*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the pink pony happily nods at @mlp_SilverS_, whips out a large mixing bowl, and sets to stirring up a special blend of cupcake batter*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Six....*Pinkie gasps* Under The Seacakes! Gimme juuuuuuuust a few minutes, okay? ^.^ *Pinkie grins at @mlp_SilverS_ and waves back at @mlp_Rocky* I'll be eeeeeextra careful to get that perfect dose of goodness!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Yepyep, ans I love, love, LOVE that enthusiasm! *she beams at @mlp_SilverS_* Whatd you have in mind? Cake? Cupcake? Frosting bowl? Cookies? Pudding?! *with each listing, she holds up a different piece of cookware*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the moonlight through the kitchen window fades, her mane springing up* We have it in ice cream, tOOOOOOoooooo! ^.^
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text:
Uhhhhhhhhh......
*Pinkie's eyes shrink at @mlp_SilverS_' mention of fish. She steps over to the ice box, flips it open, and briefly shoots the hippogriff a glance*
Don't tell anyone, but we do just in case griffons ever come around.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *her ears sag down a bit* Oh! Well, uh, what would you want to try this time, @mlp_SilverS_? You can mix anything and everything.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: What about iiiiit? *she gives @mlp_SilverS_ a curious look* Did you like what Sandbar made you try?
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Oh, uh, hi, SilverStream.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the false front of a smiling, batter-caked pony topples over, revealing a clean Pinkie Pie wiping down the counter. She abruptly peeks up at @mlp_SilverS_*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she peels one from the tip of her snoot, sets it on the edge of the drawer, and sets to work organizing by color*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie pulls open the next drawer, only to flinch as she's hit in the face with several long, deflating balloons*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Oh well. *shrugging, she flank-shuts the bottom cabinet of green and red shades*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: It's probably a nice, moonlit night, too, but hey, I have a job. At night.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the pink pony blinks down at the folded up balloons, raises a brow, and tugs the balloon from the back* Oh, I guess I was organizing.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: iiiiiiiit?
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: AH HA! Got- *Pinkie pulls to the back, only to freeze. Her back fur pricks up as her manepoof sags into a less perky, party-esque style*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she tugs open the bottom drawer and shuffles through the folded, paper thin balloons racked along the sides*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she gasps* Speaking of ballooning, we need to dust off the old hot air balloon! *Pinkie hops over to the filing cabinets nested between the favors and kazoos*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie bounces forward, springing @mlp_GummyGator along* Come on, Gummy, we've got ballooning to do!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie dips her tail into the ballpit just shy of @mlp_GummyGator's maw* All those extra cloud runoffs make it even more winter-y, and what better time to get some quality time with catching up on birthdays?!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Yepyep, the landing ballpit was a GREAT idea! ^.^ *giggling, she dolphin-leaps out and shakes a stray ball from her manepoof*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Wheeee- *the pink pony dives head-first into the ballpit at the base of the chute, sending balls about the clown-esque cavern*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: WOOHOOOOOO! *Pinkie hops belly-first onto the slide and drops down into the darkness below SCC*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *seeing a momentarily slow down, Pinkie take the opportunity to slip in back*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text:
*on the way, Pinkie catches sight of @mlp_SilverS_ approaching the lonely pony. She turns and scoots the single, plated cupcake onto @mlp_SandB's table*
There you go. I hope she likes this one.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *shrugging, Pinkie wipes her hoof clean and strolls out from behind the counter. With each step, her mane springs slightly less*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she pops the cupcake out and eyes it. Pinkie shifts the frosting glob more to the left*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the timer DINGS loudly. Slipping on a mitt, Pinkie tugs open the oven and pulls out the single, lumpy "cupcake". She grabs the small can of seaweed icing and scoops a large, shapeless glob on top*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the mare takes out the top rack of peanut butter cookies and sets them out to cool*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie tips the bowl over an empty, grey cupcake wrapper;  scoops the gelatinous batter in, and slips the single filled tray into the lower oven rack*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she stirs it in with what little is left of the cupcake batter until it has a thick, almost pudding-like consistency*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *stepping back, Pinkie digs out a large bag of wheat bran and pours a large helping in the large bowl*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she glances at the bowl with a wooden spoon sticking straight out of it* Can do, @mlp_SandB. I'll bring out over when it's ready.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: I-*a sliver of moonlight peeks through the window behind her and shines across her tailpoof* Of course. What kind of favor, @mlp_SandB?
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: I don't think so? *Pinkie slips off an oven mitt and dusts the flour off* I'm just acting like my usual, Pinkie Pie self. *she smiles a bit at @mlp_SandB* Heh.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie turns around, tray in tow* Am I? *she raises a brow at @mlp_SandB and pushes the sweets into the oven* Huh, I hadn't noticed.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *in the background, Pinkie begins work on another batch of super sugar-y treats. The pony pulls out an entire jar of peanut butter and scrapes out a large helping*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she lifts a hoof to @mlp_Chaosking* Well- *Pinkie abruptly waves over at @mlp_StrawberryB* @mlp_SIlverS_ is right, but so is @mlp__Yona, so... I think it'll be fine.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she smiles and gives each student a polite wave as they file in* Oh, yeah, Sunday night is a GREAT night for it. *Pinkie nods at @mlp_Chaosking*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie peeks over at @mlp_Chaosking* Oh, hi, Discord!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie ducks down behind the counter, slips on her mane-net, and sets a few preemptive pieces of silverware on her side of the counter*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: I see you're not the only one here. Hi, everyone! *the slightly lethargic pink pony waves to her students* And don't you worry, there's plenty.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie steps out and smiles a bit* I'm glad you approve of them, @mlp_SilverS_; I worked extra hard today!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Okay, this can work. I guess? *shrugging, she blows her less poofy mane out of her face and sneaks in back*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she makes several ticks on the wall calendar, circles a pair of dates, and hangs it back on the wall hook*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Clean stains, pay bills, get ready for the week. *she canters to the opposite side* Gosh, there's just so much to get done.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text:
*with the moon shining brightly, the pink pony frantically wipes away at the stained SCC counter*
Stains? On this counter? Oh no, no, no, not today.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *her eyes momentarily radiate with the intensity of a full moon for a moment before she pulls her head in, flops her head back, and abruptly conks out into a loud, rocking snore*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *her fur, mane, and tail prick up as a wide smile creeps across her face* OoOoOoOoOh, MoOn-Y!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *suddenly, the pink pony shoots up, eyes darting about the room. Pinkie pokes her head out the window and stares up at the celestial body above*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *yawning, Pinkie stretches out* Goodnight, Ponyville. *she peeks at the full moon, sleepily smiles, and half shuts her eyes*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the pink pony rolls onto her back, folds her hooves across her chestfuzz, and glances up at the sky*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Mrrrrrh! *she rolls her head and peeks out the window* Whew, now THAT was a day!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *humming, Pinkie bounces into her room and flops head-first onto her bed*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Nope, nothing! *she wriggles the calendar back in her mane, only for her tail to start curling. Pinkie goes wide-eyed and springs forward*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie blink-blonks as she reads the word "Caturday" written in big, purple letters over the real day of the week*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the pink pony fishes a hoof into her party poof and pulls out a calendar with a few pieces of mane stuck to it* I probably planned it, too! *she blinks* Maybeeeee?
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: I feel like something silly is gonna happen really soon. Like really, really, REALLY soon!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Lots! *she pipes up at @mlp_Lyndis*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: We'll give him an F for fun!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: That's one way to make the festival explode! *Pinkie giggles at @mlp_Emberscales* I'm totally fine!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she lifts her head, cheeks puffed. Pinkie spits out a huge glob of pumpkin, seeds and all, and shudders*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she takes @mlp_Emmyray's hoof and springs back to all fours...just as the gourd topples. Pinkie lands face first in a glob of orange*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the final step makes Pinkie tumble onto her back*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Come oooooon! *she keeps digging in with @mlp_Emmyray and @mlp_JwlBurst* Almoooooooost!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the pink pony really kicks her backpedal into overdrive, digging her hooves in with each step*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie almost immediately starts backpedaling*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text:
Hmmmmm, oh! *Pinkie bounces twice and sends herself airborne and lands atop @mlp__Smolder's pumpkin. Within moments, she's staggering into a barrel-run*
Iiiiiii diiiiiiiidn't thiiiiiink thiiiiiiis through!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: You! *hop!* can't *hop* have a chase *hop* without meeeee!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *Pinkie freezes as a faint rumbling grows. As the group, and oversized gourd roll along, Pinkie gasp, bounces out, and quickly hops after*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she gives both @mlp_Gallus and the distant @mlp_Fizzlepop a tailwave before shuffling off*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *giggling, Pinkie snags her two bags of candy* Good, because that was amazing! *Pinkie slings the oversized bundles across her back* You two have fun and be spooky!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *her mane finally poofs back into its usual form* Well, keep on doing it how you are, because that was some really GOOD scary fun! *she beams, slips back into her costume, and sips it up*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *the quivering mare peeks back at the puffy griff, only to start giggling* You got me really good! *she hops back around*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA! *her mane spindles straight out as @mlp_Gallus growl. Pinkie flat out leaps out of her costume*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Be rigth baaaaaack! *Pinkie sing-songs, drops her candy bags next to @mlp_Fizzlepop, and bounces toward the tree*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Awww, you should totally go trick of trea- *she squee-smiles* Did you say ODD CUPCAKE?! *her mane sproings to life from beneath the bug head* (@mlp_Fizzlepop)
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Where are we going anywa-- OH! How's YOUR Nightmare Night going, Fizzie? *she smiles up at @mlp_Fizzlepop* See anything SCAAAAARY?
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Thanks, @mlp_Brasve_Soul, so's yours! *Pinkie drags the bags along as @mlp_Fizzlepop drags...her*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: You sure can, /Tempest/! *winking, Pinkie snags both of her overflowing, practically bursting sacks of sweets* ^.^
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: This Nightmare Night has been beyond awesome and I love, love, love it!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she sits up and giggles at @mlp_Brave_Soul* I didn't expect any of that! *the pink pony shakes her mane, shotgunning candy around* I'm just super-dee-duper, @mlp_Fizzlepop! ^.^*Pinkie giggles*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: AAAAAAAAAAAH! *the sudden @mlp_Fizzlepop causes her to tumble into the small pile of sweets*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: AAAAAAAAAAHHHHHHHH! *both the bug-hood and her mane stand straight up at @mlp_Brave_Soul's sudden screampoof*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *pulling her bug hood down, Pinkie reaches over, snags a sourball, and tosses it in her mouth. Her face almost immediately implodes*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *one of the bags spills over a bit* Maaaaaake that super overtime.
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she drags the bags over to one of the nearby benches and flops across the stone sitting slab* Whew! If time is candy, then I'm doing overtime!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: HRRRRRK! *Pinkie haphazardly bounces through the center, dragging along two full bags of candy*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *nodding, Pinkie join in on the frightening, but every attempt ends up being more goofy than terrifying. She tries to hiss, only to squeak*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Destroy you? *she half smiles* Now, why would I ever do that?
Name: Pinkie Pie

Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she knocks on both doors. Within moments, both swing open. On one side, a mare steps out with a candy bowl, on the other, a stallion in a scarecrow mask stands with a large broom*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she smiles back at @mlp_Asphodel* Well, you're doing Nightmare Night with us, so that'e enough for me! *she bounces up to the double doors with the group*

Text: *Pinkie stares in awe momentarily* Lucky for you, the next house is a double doozie: the mare /loves/ giving out candy, but the stallion likes swatting brooms!

Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: Trick or treeeeeat! *Pinkie holds out her pillowcase* ^.^
Name: Pinkie Pie

Text: *she slings her candy sack* Then let's make sure you do! *Pinkie pulls the bug up to the front*

Text: *her costume wings buzz in response. Pinkie pulls the bug-hood back up* Of course I'm scared, silly; it's Nightmare Night time, so everything's got that scary air! *Pinkie abruptly grabs @mlp_Asphodel's hoof* Now, c'mon, time is candy, bug sister!

Text: *she leans toward @mlp_Asphodel and whisper shouts* You should totally come trick of treating with us. It's fun!
Name: Pinkie Pie

Name: Pinkie Pie

Name: Pinkie Pie

Name: Pinkie Pie

Text:
*she holds out her pillowcase with the conglomerate of plastic pumpkins and other sacks* 
Trick or treeeeeeeat! ^.^ *her tail rustles back toward @mlp_Asphodel*
Name: Pinkie Pie

Fast forward about a year, and I made my first OC.
